  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (80df71f 2023-09-26T18:05:26.004416000Z)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\n`forge init --template`\n\n### Operating System\n\nmacOS (Intel)\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nIssue for tracking PR #5911\r\n\r\n`forge init --template` clones a repo, then deletes the entire .git directory so that it can re-initialize the repository with a single commit in its history.\r\n\r\nThis clobbers submodule tracking and commits entire recursed submodules directly to the git tree.\r\n\r\n",
